;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;于是手工绘制&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:18px;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:18px;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;各种框尺寸方面可能会有&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:18px;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;1-5CM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:18px;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;的误差&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:18px;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#000000;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:18px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;请&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color:#666666;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:18px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;完全不能接受一点误差的亲们谨慎购买&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:18px;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#666666;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:24px;color:#E53333;&quot;&gt;【关于发票】&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:18px;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;如需开发票的亲们&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:18px;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:18px;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;请主动与我们客服联系&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&